E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I've walked that road. Al Di Napoli knows pain.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我也是这样的。Al Di Napoli懂你的难处。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~That's a shame, brother. Al feels your pain.
~z~The restraining part of my brain is long dead.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我脑子里的节制模块早就死了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Sweet. Take me to the Amdram, bro? I got people to entertain.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~好哇。带我去Amdram剧院吧，兄弟。观众等着我呢。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Boss, you mind heading over to Hercules? Al Di Napoli is asking for you specifically.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~老板，介意跑一趟大力神吗？Al Di Napoli点名叫你过去。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Who you take me for, L? Bruce Spade or someone?
~z~I don't know, man. Might be. I ain't remembered a performance yet.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~不知道啊。应该吧。我也忘了演的啥了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Then fuck it. I ain't ever gonna come back to this town. I don't care what my agent promises me.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~滚他妈的。我也不会回来了，也不在乎经纪人跟我保证啥了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~One of them's a Police Chief, and the other guy did time for tax evasion. I was lucky to get out.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~其中一个当了警长，另一个因为逃税去蹲监狱了。我运气还不错。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Fucking she-males to see what it feels like, taking apart hotel room TVs to see where pay-per-view comes from,
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~出于好奇去操人妖，拆开酒店的电视研究收费节目的原理，

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Don't worry, man. I'll take the heat for this if we go down. You won't see any of it.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~没事，哥们。被抓了我来担责。保证把你撇干净。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I feel you, bro. The Italian kids I grew up with became cops or ended up in the big house.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我懂你，兄弟。和我一起长大的意大利孩子不是成了警察就是住上了大别墅。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~That ain't a good idea. Chill out.
~z~Lopez! What you doing here, bitch? I thought you was out the game.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~Lopez！你这逼咋在这儿呢？你不是洗手不干了吗。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Of course, man. Let's get the fuck out of here.
~z~No, I'm joking. You look okay... just about.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~没，我开玩笑的。你看起来还好...挺好的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Nah, bro. Of course I ain't. I'm implying that you fall into both.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~啊，兄弟。当然没有了。我是说你两个都占了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~We having enough trouble maintaining the operation here, Al. I don't think we ready to expand things.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~现在保住自由城的店都够呛，Al。不太可能开新店。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I'm on the path, motherfucker. And Al Di Napoli will beat the monkey off his back.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我都在路上了，操你妈的。Al Di Napoli会摆脱困境的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Yeah, well... I was, but we had these two Italian dudes in our class.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~对，呃...确实是，但我们班有两个意大利人。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Shit, man. I thought this work was subtle - I paid for the "natural look".
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~妈的，哥们。我藏得不够深吗？专门花钱做的「自然造型」。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~ Al, it's great to see you again, man.
~z~I'm just a little highly strung right now, L. I'm sorry.
~z~Back in the day I was a kick boxer.
~z~This thing ain't happening, D . We ran into an issue.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~事情解决不了了，D。这里出问题了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I'm sorry, bro. It don't look like you getting your shit.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~不好意思，兄弟。看来你拿不了货了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~It looks like we're in the clear, Al.
~z~Gimme a gun, bro. I wanna pop some of these motherfuckers. I've done it in lots of films.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~给我把枪，兄弟。我一枪一个傻逼条子。电影里我经常这么干。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~What you doing in here, bro? I didn't think this was your scene.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你在大力神干啥呢，兄弟？这不是你会来的地方吧。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Fine with me. Enjoy the high life.
~z~What the producers gonna think if you get arrested on a school night?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~要是你在工作前一天被捕，制片人会怎么想？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Don't run on my account, L. I can handle some time on the inside.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~没必要带我逃跑，L。我不介意蹲几年牢房的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I fear that day ain't far off, Al.
~z~Sanity, bro? I'd hate to think what you'd be like somewhere else.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~保持清醒，兄弟？很难想象你在其他地方的情况。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I hope you ain't implying that I fall into either one of them stereotypes, L.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~希望你不是想说我是二者之一，L。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~The Herc's got some vibe, bro. Those people are real.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~大力神才有氛围，兄弟。大家都很真实。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Yo, I'm getting some crank off an asshole up here. Can you help me out?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~哟，我跟人约好在这儿取货。你能帮帮我吗？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I hope it's nothing serious, boss. You take care.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~希望没出大事，老板。你多保重。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I'd be a fucking train wreck, bro. Vice is the only city in the US worth sticking in.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我就是个废物，兄弟。罪城是美国唯一值得去的城市了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~What the fuck? Al Di Napoli can fight.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~说啥呢？Al Di Napoli有两下子的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Your chances of lasting a round in the cage after a week long meth binge are slim to none. Stick to acting.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~嗑药嗨上一周之后，你都没机会跟别人斗上一回合。老实当演员吧。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~That was twenty years ago, Al. Things kind of different now.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~那都是二十年前了，Al。现在不一样了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Fuck. We ain't getting arrested. Let's go!
~z~They don't get special treatment, I don't want it neither. Man of the fucking people. That's Al Di Napoli for you.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~他们没有特殊待遇，我也不想要。与大众打成一片。这就是我Al Di Napoli。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~What the fuck do you know, man? That shit is hard. And no one said nothing about meth. Fuck you.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你他妈懂个屁？这可难了。谁跟你提吸毒了。操你妈的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You get conceited motherfuckers in Hercules too, Al.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~大力神也有自以为是的傻逼啊，Al。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Sometimes it keeps me up at night thinking about them bloody faces, and broken bones I caused.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~想到对手血淋淋的脸和被我打断的骨头，我就睡不好觉。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~No, man, a crisis of just about everything else. I'll tell you about it some other time. Guy is deranged.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~不是，是别的危机。改天再告诉你吧，这人疯了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~That's real nice of you, Al, but my priors are gonna give these guys plenty of shit to throw at me.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你真好，Al。但我有前科，条子不会轻易放过我的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Respectfully, I ain't gonna get no implants to make me look like a swollen nut sack.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~恕我直言，我可不想整容整成屌面人。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Everyone gotta do this shit now. First step on the comeback road. Make the motherfuckers think you serious.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~也是不得已而为之啊。这是复出之路的第一步，必须让大家看见你是认真的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Yeah, but they're a lot more honest about their drug habits. And the motherfucker don't close!
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~是有，但他们对自己的吸毒史就实诚多了。他们还不躲藏！

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I don't need looking after, bro. I'm just here to get fucked up with the homos.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~没必要关照我，兄弟。我就是来跟男同喝酒的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~People paid a hundred dollars to see me, they gonna be pissed if I pass out on stage.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~大家花一百块钱看我演出，我要是上台就晕了，他们会生气的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Three days, I think. It's kind of a blur.
~z~It don't feel like you found "the way", bro.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你不像是找到了「那条路」啊，兄弟。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You live in Vice now, don't you?
~z~That we do. What was it, boss? Crisis of sexuality?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你回来吧。都干啥了，老板？遇到性危机了？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I do my best work when I'm three days into a bender. You don't wanna see this shit sober. Believe me.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~大了以后再上台效果才好。清醒了反而演得没意思，相信我。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You start doing weird shit when you get old, bro. Real weird shit.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~年纪大了就会做一些奇怪的事，兄弟。真的很怪。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Shit boss, I take it things didn't go too good. Go chill out. We'll talk soon.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~妈的，老板，这事不对劲啊。最近避避风头，咱晚点聊。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Big Al's a legend, L. Have fun.
~z~Then I'm gonna have to go looking for other sources, L.
~z~Fuck the producers, man. They can stick my "scale" paycheck up their asses.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~操他妈的制片人。他们可以把我的底薪支票贴自己屁股上。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I went for tax reasons and stayed for my sanity.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我因为税务原因过去的，在那儿还能保持清醒。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~That's what makes it a spiritual home for degenerates.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~所以那里成为了社会败类的精神家园。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You were uptown buying some shit and they busted us.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你来城外进货，被他们盯上了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You a characterful dude, Al. You don't need to do that to your face.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你这人很有特色，Al。没必要在脸上动刀子。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Blood suckin' cocksuckers and their eight shows a week. Slaves work less than me.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~不当人的吸血鬼，一周要演八场戏。我比奴隶还辛苦。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Day before the day before yesterday I was banging some girl then I'm here and, shit, I don't know.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~大前天我跟哪个姑娘干了一炮，然后去了夜店，然后...妈的，不记得了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Can you give me a ride up to Vespucci U, my brother.
~z~Five years at the top of my game - any girl, any guy, any cat, any dog, all the drugs I could take.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我在业内风光了五年，妹子、兄弟、阿猫、阿狗，还有各种毒品。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I heard it was just old retired fraudsters and plastic party people.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~听说那里都是退休的老诈骗犯和伪君子。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I've dealt with that Big Al thing. You need me back?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~Al大哥这边忙完了。需要我回去吗？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~We got to get out of here. Come on!
~z~Yeah, well. I'm amazed you alive then.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~是吗，你还活着真是一个奇迹。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Think of this as research, bro. You can use this the next time you play a criminal.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~今天就当是采风了，兄弟。作为以后扮演罪犯的经验。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~No one parties like a bunch of homos, L. They've got it down.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~男同派对可是人间一绝，L。别有情调。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~The days of assistants are long gone for me. I'm a fighter, man. I'll die on the streets.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我早没有助理了。我现在是战士，哥们。死也要死在街头。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Coño. I knew I shouldn't have gone on that run, bro.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~妈的，我就知道不该跑这趟的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~What's happening? Why are the cops after us?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~怎么回事？为啥条子追着咱们？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Things ain't exactly gone to plan here, Dess. You know what I mean?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~这边事情不太顺利，Dess。懂我意思吧？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~No, I ain't got the "hook up". I grew up round here and it's a small place. You tend to know some bad dudes.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~没，有啥「往来」啊。我就在这长大的，大家都是邻居。认识些坏人在所难免。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~There he is. Let's get the fuck out of here.
~z~Thanks a lot, bro. I'll call you in a few days in advance so you can sober up for the performance.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~那多谢了，兄弟。过几天我提前给你打电话，好让你清醒下准备演出。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Sounds ominous, bro. I'll check it out.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~感觉没啥好事，兄弟。我去看看吧。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Have a good time at Hercules, boss.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~祝你在大力神玩得开心，老板。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~When's the last time you were alowed to buy poppers and a beer at 9am?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~上次能白天九点出来买毒品和酒是多久以前了？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Bro, when are you and Tony gonna expand the operation to Vice? We need you down there.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~兄弟，你跟Tony啥时候到罪城开店？那里需要你们。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You into fighting, L, or is that some bullshit I heard.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你在打架赚钱吗，L，还是说这是谣言？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~It ain't the first time I've run from the cops, L. Fuckers been on me forever. Watching me sleep and stuff.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我也不是头一次被条子追了，L。条子一直都盯着我，睡觉都要监视。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~So am I. But Al Di Napoli he's a street fighter. That's his thing. Fighting the streets.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我也觉得。但Al Di Napoli是个街头战士。在街头战斗，那是他的事业。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~The old Liberty City will be dead soon.
~z~Yo, man, you got to take me up to Vespucci University.
~z~Thank you very much, my brother. There's a comp on the door whenever you want it.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~太谢谢你了，好兄弟。给你张入场券，随时可以来看。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~That what I look like? Motherfucker! I'm gonna kill that doctor when I see him next.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我看起来是那样的吗？操你妈的！下次再见到这医生我就杀了他。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I didn't even think you were a theater actor, Al.
~z~Hey bro, things got weird on that thing I was dealing with. I'm gonna lay low for a while.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~嘿兄弟。这次的事不太对劲。我要避会儿风头了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Oscar Gomez! That you, motherfucker? Shit, bro, I'd love to stay and catch up, but we need to pick up and go.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~Oscar Gomez！是你啊，你妈逼的？妈的，兄弟，我也想跟你多聊几句，但咱得赶紧拿货走人。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~How'd you know that dealer, L? You got the hook up?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你咋认识那个毒贩，L？你俩有往来？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I'd heard you were over here doing a play or something? We thought we might see you at Maisonette.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~听说你是来自由城演戏的？我还以为你会来9号豪宅。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~No problem, man. Let me handle it.
~z~None of the Los Santos bullshit, or the Liberty neuroses. It's fucking pure.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~没洛圣都那么扯淡，也没自由城这么神经。巨他妈纯。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Shit, L. Okay. I'll get on damage control.
~z~Yeah. It's a good thing that mixed arts martial shit wasn't popular in my time. I woulda gone pro, man. I woulda.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~对。还好我那个时候不流行综合格斗。否则我就是职业选手了，职业的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Oye, how long you been up for? You seem kind of wired.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~喂，你嗨了多久啊？看起来有点上头了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I can't tell no more what's true and what stuff I made up in my head. Man, I am fried right now.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我已经分不清哪些是真的，哪些是臆想的了。天哪，我要炸了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Shit. There was a time police wouldn't go above Topaz Street. What's happened to LC?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~妈的，当年警察不会来Topez街以北的啊。自由城怎么了？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I don't know what he's doing. But he wants you to be doing it with him.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我也不知道他来干啥，但他就是叫你过去找他。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~It's all part of the passage of life, my brother. You'll see. It's kind of beautiful.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~这都是人生的一部分，好兄弟。你会懂的。也是一种美。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Yo, man, I heard you was from some affluent Jewish neighborhood.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~哟，哥们，你不是来自富裕的犹太社区吗？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~ Al, bro, it's been a while.
~z~You should tell me if you coming down to Herc, bro. I could have you looked after.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你来大力神咋不跟我说一声呢，兄弟。我还能过来关照你。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Come on, brother. I wouldn't be here if I had self-restraint.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~得了吧，兄弟。我要是有自制力就不会有今天。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~What's the deal with this shit, Al? Ain't you got an assistant to buy drugs for you?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~搞什么啊，Al？没有帮你拿货的助理吗？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Okay, boss. Anyone asks, I ain't seen you.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~好的，老板。有人问起来我就说没见过你。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~I'm sorry, bro. Theater ain't usually my thing. This play any good?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~不好意思，兄弟。我不怎么去剧院的。这场戏好看吗？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~fisting yourself, dammit. Al's done his time in Hotel Batshit Crazy.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~甚至给自己一拳，妈的。Al一直都是这种疯疯癫癫的状态。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Yo, D. Shit kinda fucked up here, man. Can you cover for me?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~哟，D。事情有点搞砸了，哥们。你能帮我瞒过去吗？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Why ain't you come to see me at the theater, yet?
~z~I'm a nominee. Al Di Napoli is somebody.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~我是候选人。Al Di Napoli是个大人物。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~Sorry, bro. I didn't mean no offence.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~不好意思，兄弟。我不是故意的。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You're the motherfuckers who keep the club open 24. What's a man meant to do if he don't get kicked out a place?
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你们夜店24小时不打烊怪我喽。不把我赶出来，我不待在店里还去哪？

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~You don't wanna be no cage fighter, Al.
~z~What's Al doing at Hercules? He ain't gay.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~Al在大力神干啥？他不是基佬吧。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~It's true. Well, was true, at least. I don't take it too serious now.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~是有这事。打过一段时间。现在不那么上心了。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~you go to a doctor and tell him you'll pay him anything to make you look like you did two decades ago.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~你还会去找医生，让他把你整成年轻二十岁的脸，多少钱都行。

E2Tm7AU.original: ~z~No offence, L, but that place ain't my scene no more. Fucking stuck up pieces of shit in there.
E2Tm7AU.translated: ~z~恕我直言，L，但我已经厌倦豪宅了。净是些自以为是的臭傻逼。
